{"tid":240910,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"勿提L'Oréal group&勿助長代購&第一頁有懶人包 化妝品及護膚品討論區#47","createTime":"2017-05-12T18:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T18:26:55.000Z","uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"942b4c830b870f29313768caf29e38c9666b9cbb","tid":240910,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"毋忘港恥<br />\n勿 提 L'Or&eacute;al Group <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLANCOME 事件重溫<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2FLanc%C3%B4me%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E6%9C%83%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3f98f8ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/Lanc&ocirc;me取消何韻詩演唱會風波</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[勿助長代購] 自己化妝品自己買！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/226858/page/21?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/226858/page/21?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望連登妝post可以保持返高登幾十個post嘅良好風氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問問題前睇清楚#1及懶人包 <br />\n(e.g. 花水問題及其他熱門產品)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好Google左先 對想問嘅野有基本了解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 善用關鍵字搜尋e.g. Google打「xxx lihkg」或「xxx site:<a href=\"http://lihkg.com\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com</a>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講清楚自己要求同基本資料<br />\n（例如：乾性皮膚想搵一隻滋潤光澤型嘅粉底霜，依家用緊XXX 覺得好乾...）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如閱讀後有其他問題可以上POST一齊討論 唔好咁懶豬做伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懶 人 包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊懶人包比人close左<br />\n宜家有新懶人包不過要比D時間重建 <br />\n格式同內容會漸漸加 希望大家等待<br />\n如果有其他絲打想幫人或者分享都歡迎PM GMAIL比波耶波囉咪 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外大家可以留意下animal testing呢樣野, 有好多香港有既品牌都有做動物測試, 例如cdp, dior, shiseido, tom ford, fresh<br />\n想知個brand係咪cruelty-free有幾個方法:<br />\n1)<br />\n如果間公司係中國有實店, 咁佢一定有test on animals, <br />\n因為呢個係中國法律永規定<br />\n2)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.crueltyfreekitty.com%2Fcompanies-that-test-on-animals%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=dee1dc71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.crueltyfreekitty.com/companies-that-test-on-animals/</a><br />\n3)<br />\n<a href=\"http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.peta.org%2Fcruelty-free-company-search%2Findex.aspx&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2Bhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=5f29bcbd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://features.peta.org/cruelty-free-company-search/index.aspx</a><br />\n4)<br />\nGoogle<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 溫馨提示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為方便爬文 請大家喺加左密既包膠後面加返keywords<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外提大家唔好quote太多圖 記得順便del img code 以免金剛棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1001左果個記得copy返呢度 D 野